raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.0-7" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-sf
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/sf_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/sf/sf_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: d0731fab9438d73a55af7232f0474b36f4b2a4e6d66adaa141632f4a60265453

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 6
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}            # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_cxx') }}      # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}grep              # [win]
    - {{ posix }}autoconf
    - {{ posix }}automake          # [not win]
    - {{ posix }}automake-wrapper  # [win]
    - {{ posix }}pkg-config
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
    - sysroot_linux-64 2.17  # [linux64]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-dbi >=0.8
    - r-rcpp >=0.12.18
    - r-classint >=0.4_1
    - r-magrittr
    - r-units >=0.6_0
    - r-s2
    - libgdal  # [not win]
    - proj  # [not win]
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-dbi >=0.8
    - r-rcpp >=0.12.18
    - r-classint >=0.4_1
    - r-magrittr
    - r-units >=0.6_0
    - r-s2
    - libgdal  # [not win]
    - proj  # [not win]

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('sf')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('sf')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/r-spatial/sf/, https://r-spatial.github.io/sf/
  license: GPL-2.0-only OR MIT
  summary: Support for simple features, a standardized way to encode spatial vector data. Binds to 'GDAL' for reading and writing data, to 'GEOS' for geometrical operations, and to 'PROJ' for projection conversions and datum transformations.
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/MIT
    - LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - mingwandroid
